<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>UNITECH ERP - Landing Page</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link href="/css/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script defer src="/js/back-navigation.js"></script>
  <script defer src="/js/public-visit-tracker.js"></script>
  <style>
    :root {
      --brand-blue: #1E3A8A;
      --brand-orange: #F97316;
      --bg-light: #F3F4F6;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--bg-light); }

    .landing-loader {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 90;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1E3A8A);
      transition: opacity .45s ease, visibility .45s ease;
    }
    .landing-loader.hidden {
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
    }
    .loader-mark {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 78px;
      height: 78px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: white;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.16);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      animation: loaderPulse 1.1s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes loaderPulse {
      from { transform: scale(.95); }
      to { transform: scale(1.04); }
    }

    .smart-nav {
      transition: padding .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease, background-color .25s ease;
    }
    .smart-nav.scrolled {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .1);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
    }

    .hero-shell {
      background: linear-gradient(130deg, #0f172a, #1E3A8A, #1e40af, #0f172a);
      background-size: 280% 280%;
      animation: gradientShift 22s ease infinite;
    }
    @keyframes gradientShift {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    .hero-network {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      opacity: .22;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-network path {
      stroke-dasharray: 12 10;
      animation: pathMove 14s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pathMove {
      from { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
      to { stroke-dashoffset: 220; }
    }

    .hero-anim {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(26px);
      animation: heroIn .75s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) forwards;
    }
    .hero-anim.delay-1 { animation-delay: .18s; }
    .hero-anim.delay-2 { animation-delay: .34s; }
    .hero-anim.delay-3 { animation-delay: .52s; }
    @keyframes heroIn {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity .65s ease, transform .65s ease;
    }
    .reveal.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .reveal.zoom {
      transform: scale(.96);
    }
    .reveal.zoom.show {
      transform: scale(1);
    }

    .feature-card {
      transition: transform .26s ease, box-shadow .26s ease, border-color .26s ease;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-7px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(15, 23, 42, .16);
      border-color: rgba(30, 58, 138, .2);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      transition: color .25s ease, background-color .25s ease;
    }
    .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
      color: white;
      background-color: var(--brand-orange);
    }

    .price-card {
      position: relative;
      transition: transform .26s ease, box-shadow .26s ease;
    }
    .price-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(15, 23, 42, .18);
    }
    .price-card.recommended {
      border: 2px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, .55);
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }
    .price-card.recommended::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -2px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, .35);
      animation: borderGlow 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    @keyframes borderGlow {
      0%, 100% { opacity: .35; }
      50% { opacity: .9; }
    }
    .pulse-btn {
      animation: softPulse 1.9s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes softPulse {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(249, 115, 22, .3); }
      70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 12px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0); }
    }

    .cta-btn {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform .2s ease, background-color .2s ease;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      background-color: var(--brand-orange);
    }
    .cta-btn::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transform: scale(0);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.36);
      left: var(--rx, 50%);
      top: var(--ry, 50%);
      transition: transform .45s ease, opacity .45s ease;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .cta-btn.ripple::after {
      transform: scale(26);
      opacity: 1;
      transition: transform .5s ease, opacity .7s ease;
    }

    .counter {
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; }
      .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
      .hero-anim { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800" data-back-fallback="/vitrine">
  <div id="landing-loader" class="landing-loader">
    <div class="loader-mark">U</div>
  </div>

  <header id="smart-nav" class="smart-nav sticky top-0 z-30 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-4 py-3">
      <a href="/vitrine" class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-[#1E3A8A] text-white font-black">U</div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-500">UNITECH</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#1E3A8A]">ERP SaaS</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <nav class="hidden gap-5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 md:flex">
        <a href="/entreprise" class="hover:text-[#1E3A8A]">Entreprise</a>
        <a href="#vision" class="hover:text-[#1E3A8A]">Vision</a>
        <a href="#features" class="hover:text-[#1E3A8A]">Fonctionnalites</a>
        <a href="#roles" class="hover:text-[#1E3A8A]">Utilisateurs</a>
        <a href="#pricing" class="hover:text-[#1E3A8A]">Tarifs</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <a href="<%= downloadLinks && downloadLinks.windows ? downloadLinks.windows : '/download/desktop/windows' %>" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Telecharger Windows (.exe)</a>
        <a href="<%= downloadLinks && downloadLinks.mac ? downloadLinks.mac : '/download/desktop/mac' %>" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Telecharger Mac (.dmg)</a>
        <a href="/entreprise" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Entreprise</a>
        <% if (currentUser && currentUser.role === 'superadmin') { %>
          <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="cta-btn rounded-xl bg-[#1E3A8A] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white">Dashboard Admin</a>
        <% } else if (currentUser && (currentUser.role === 'school_admin' || currentUser.role === 'staff')) { %>
          <a href="/dashboard" class="cta-btn rounded-xl bg-[#1E3A8A] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white">Mon Tableau de Bord</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Connexion</a>
          <a href="/register" class="cta-btn rounded-xl bg-[#F97316] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white">Creer un etablissement</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-shell relative overflow-hidden">
      <svg class="hero-network" viewBox="0 0 1200 420" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0,200 C140,150 220,250 340,200 C460,150 560,260 700,210 C840,160 980,250 1200,180" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.2"/>
        <path d="M0,270 C160,210 260,320 380,260 C500,200 640,320 760,250 C880,180 1020,280 1200,230" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="absolute -top-16 -right-16 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[#F97316]/20 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -left-10 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-4 py-20 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] lg:items-center">
        <div class="text-white">
          <p class="hero-anim mb-4 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
            UNITECH ERP
          </p>
          <h1 class="hero-anim delay-1 text-4xl font-black leading-tight md:text-5xl">
            Solution ERP Intelligente pour Etablissements Modernes
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-anim delay-2 mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base text-slate-200 md:text-lg">
            Gestion scolaire, abonnements, maintenance et solutions technologiques integrees.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-anim delay-3 mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="/register" class="cta-btn rounded-xl bg-[#F97316] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg">Creer un etablissement</a>
            <a href="/login" class="cta-btn rounded-xl border border-white/30 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/10">Se connecter</a>
            <a href="<%= downloadLinks && downloadLinks.windows ? downloadLinks.windows : '/download/desktop/windows' %>" class="cta-btn rounded-xl border border-white/30 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/10">Desktop Windows (.exe)</a>
            <a href="<%= downloadLinks && downloadLinks.mac ? downloadLinks.mac : '/download/desktop/mac' %>" class="cta-btn rounded-xl border border-white/30 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/10">Desktop Mac (.dmg)</a>
            <a href="/admin/login" class="cta-btn rounded-xl border border-white/30 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/10">Espace Admin</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal rounded-2xl bg-white/95 p-5 shadow-2xl">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-slate-500">ERP SaaS International</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1E3A8A]">Plateforme unifiee</h2>
          <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-3"><p class="text-slate-500">Ecoles</p><p class="counter text-xl font-bold text-[#1E3A8A]" data-counter-target="<%= Number(metrics && metrics.totalSchools ? metrics.totalSchools : 0) %>">0+</p></div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-3"><p class="text-slate-500">Eleves</p><p class="counter text-xl font-bold text-[#1E3A8A]" data-counter-target="<%= Number(metrics && metrics.totalEleves ? metrics.totalEleves : 0) %>">0+</p></div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-3"><p class="text-slate-500">Satisfaction</p><p class="counter text-xl font-bold text-[#1E3A8A]" data-counter-target="<%= Number(metrics && Number.isFinite(metrics.satisfaction) ? metrics.satisfaction : 0) %>" data-counter-suffix="%">0%</p></div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-3"><p class="text-slate-500">Disponibilite</p><p class="counter text-xl font-bold text-[#1E3A8A]" data-counter-target="<%= Number(metrics && Number.isFinite(metrics.disponibilite) ? metrics.disponibilite : 0) %>" data-counter-suffix="%">0%</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-3 text-xs text-slate-600">
            Visiteurs vitrine/entreprise: <strong><%= Number(visitorStats && visitorStats.totalVisits ? visitorStats.totalVisits : 0).toLocaleString('fr-FR') %></strong>
            (<%= Number(visitorStats && visitorStats.uniqueVisitors ? visitorStats.uniqueVisitors : 0).toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> uniques)
            - Aujourd'hui: <strong><%= Number(visitorStats && visitorStats.visitsToday ? visitorStats.visitsToday : 0).toLocaleString('fr-FR') %></strong>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-[#F97316]/30 bg-[#FFF7ED] p-3 text-xs text-slate-700">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[#C2410C]">Acces demo en ligne</p>
            <p class="mt-1">Email: <strong>demo@gmail.com</strong></p>
            <p>Mot de passe: <strong>demo@</strong></p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-slate-500">Demo disponible uniquement en ligne.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10">
      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#1E3A8A]">Essentiel a savoir avant de commencer</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Ces informations sont les plus consultees par les nouveaux visiteurs.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="#pricing" class="cta-btn rounded-xl bg-[#F97316] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white">Voir les tarifs</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Fonctionnalites principales</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Gestion eleves, classes, enseignants, matieres et absences</li>
              <li>Notes, bulletins PDF, paiements scolaires, depenses et salaires</li>
              <li>Emplois du temps, affectations, dashboard et rapports</li>
              <li>Setup assiste, import Excel et OCR selon le plan</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-emerald-800">Plan annuel avec reduction</h3>
            <%
              const byCode = {};
              (plans || []).forEach((p) => { byCode[String(p.code || '').toLowerCase()] = p; });
              const pb = byCode.basic || {};
              const ps = byCode.pro || {};
              const pp = byCode.premium || {};
              const ecoB = Math.max((Number(pb.price_monthly || 0) * 12) - Number(pb.price_annual || 0), 0);
              const ecoS = Math.max((Number(ps.price_monthly || 0) * 12) - Number(ps.price_annual || 0), 0);
              const ecoP = Math.max((Number(pp.price_monthly || 0) * 12) - Number(pp.price_annual || 0), 0);
            %>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-emerald-900">
              <li>Basic: <strong><%= Number(pb.price_annual || 0).toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA/an</strong> (economie <%= ecoB.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA)</li>
              <li>Smart: <strong><%= Number(ps.price_annual || 0).toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA/an</strong> (economie <%= ecoS.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA)</li>
              <li>Premium: <strong><%= Number(pp.price_annual || 0).toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA/an</strong> (economie <%= ecoP.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA)</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-xl border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Nouvelle fonctionnalite: Executables Desktop</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
              UNITECH ERP est disponible en application installee sur vos machines Windows (.exe) et macOS (.dmg).
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Ouverture rapide depuis le bureau, sans navigateur</li>
              <li>Meilleure stabilite pour un usage quotidien en etablissement</li>
              <li>Mises a jour automatiques pour rester sur la derniere version</li>
              <li>Confort de travail optimise pour les postes administratifs</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <a href="<%= downloadLinks && downloadLinks.windows ? downloadLinks.windows : '/download/desktop/windows' %>" class="rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Installer Windows</a>
              <a href="<%= downloadLinks && downloadLinks.mac ? downloadLinks.mac : '/download/desktop/mac' %>" class="rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Installer macOS</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="vision" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#1E3A8A]">Notre Vision</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-slate-600">
          UNITECH est une entreprise technologique moderne specialisee dans les solutions digitales, la maintenance industrielle,
          la formation technique et l'innovation en mecatronique. Nous construisons des outils fiables, scalables et orientes impact,
          avec un accompagnement client fort, une expertise technique de terrain et une approche d'innovation continue.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4"><p class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Fiabilite</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4"><p class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Innovation</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4"><p class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Expertise technique</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4"><p class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Accompagnement client</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-16">
      <h2 class="reveal text-3xl font-black text-[#1E3A8A]">Fonctionnalites ERP</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <% const features = ['Gestion eleves','Gestion classes','Gestion enseignants','Paiements & finances','Statistiques intelligentes','Gestion abonnements','Acces multi-roles','Securite des donnees']; %>
        <% features.forEach((f, idx) => { %>
          <article class="feature-card reveal rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-lg" data-reveal-delay="<%= idx * 70 %>">
            <div class="feature-icon mb-3 grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-[#1E3A8A]/10 text-[#1E3A8A]">+</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold"><%= f %></h3>
          </article>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="feature-card reveal rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-lg" data-reveal-delay="120">
          <div class="mb-2 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700">OCR photo</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Saisie des notes par photo</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            L'enseignant remplit une fiche de notes, prend une photo, puis le systeme lit automatiquement le texte
            (matricule + note) pour pre-remplir les resultats.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Fonctionnement de base: 1) photo nette, 2) reconnaissance OCR, 3) verification rapide, 4) validation.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card reveal rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-lg" data-reveal-delay="180">
          <div class="mb-2 inline-flex rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700">Setup assiste</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Demarrage guide de l'etablissement</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Un assistant pas-a-pas configure les classes, eleves et notes pour demarrer rapidement sans reglages
            techniques complexes.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Fonctionnement de base: 1) creation des classes, 2) import/ajout des eleves, 3) import/saisie des notes.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

  

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-16">
      <h2 class="reveal text-3xl font-black text-[#1E3A8A]">Synchronisation Web / Desktop</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="feature-card reveal rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-lg" data-reveal-delay="60">
          <div class="mb-2 inline-flex rounded-full bg-indigo-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-700">Web app</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">Acces direct au Postgres central</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Depuis le navigateur (mobile ou tablette), les utilisateurs lisent et ecrivent en temps reel sur la base centrale.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li>• Zero installation</li>
            <li>• Donnees toujours a jour</li>
            <li>• Ideal pour direction/enseignants en deplacement</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card reveal rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-lg" data-reveal-delay="120">
          <div class="mb-2 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700">Desktop offline-first</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">SQLite local + sync auto</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">L'executable Electron travaille en local (SQLite) et synchronise vers le Postgres central des que le reseau revient.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li>• Fonctionne sans connexion</li>
            <li>• Push/pull auto a chaque reconnexion</li>
            <li>• Cycle planifie toutes les 15 minutes</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card reveal rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-lg" data-reveal-delay="180">
          <div class="mb-2 inline-flex rounded-full bg-orange-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-700">Concordance</div>
